---
layout: main
description: "Keeping your data secure and private is important to us at Sembark. We processing your personal data in a secure,
fair, and we are transparent about our practices as a business"
showChatBox: false
showAnnouncement: false
sitemap:
  changefreq: monthly
  priority: 0.20
---

<main class="mx-auto">
  <div class="text-center py-24 bg-indigo-800 px-4">
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl mb-8 text-indigo-50 font-bold">
      Terms, Privacy and Procedures
    </h1>
    <p class="max-w-2xl text-lg mx-auto text-indigo-100">
      We're committed to keeping your data secure, your private information
      private, and being transparent about our practices as a business.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="bg-white relative">
    <div class="py-24 container mx-auto px-4 space-y-12 lg:flex lg:space-y-0">
      <aside class="lg:w-64 lg:sticky top-0 z-10">
        <nav class="flex flex-col space-y-4 p-4 rounded font-medium">
          <a
            href="/legal/terms"
            class="block w-full py-2 px-3 rounded {{ 'text-gray-900 bg-gray-200 ' if key === 'terms' else
                   'text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-800'}}"
            >Terms of Service</a
          >
          <a
            href="/legal/privacy"
            class="block w-full py-2 px-3 rounded {{ 'text-gray-900 bg-gray-200 ' if key === 'privacy' else
                   'text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-800'}}"
            >Privacy Policy</a
          >
          <a
            href="/legal/security"
            class="block w-full py-2 px-3 rounded {{ 'text-gray-900 bg-gray-200 ' if key === 'security' else
                   'text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-800'}}"
            >Security</a
          >
          <a
            href="/legal/cookie-policy"
            class="block w-full py-2 px-3 rounded {{ 'text-gray-900 bg-gray-200 ' if key === 'cookie' else
                   'text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-800'}}"
            >Cookie Policy</a
          >
          <a
            href="/legal/sub-processors"
            class="block w-full py-2 px-3 rounded {{ 'text-gray-900 bg-gray-200 ' if key === 'subprocessors' else
                   'text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-800'}}"
            >List of Sub-processors</a
          >
        </nav>
      </aside>
      <div class="flex-1 pl-4">
        <div>
          <article class="prose lg:prose-lg mx-auto">
            {{ content | safe }}
            <hr />
            <p>
              Questions about the Terms, Privacy and Procedures should be sent
              to
              <a href="mailto:{{ meta.legalEmail }}">{{ meta.legalEmail }}</a>
            </p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</main>
